long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Private Discuss is a unified videoconferencing solution that offers instant messaging, videoconferencing and simple online meetings into one easy-to-use platform. Our solution offers high quality video, audio and screen-sharing experience across all platforms.

The Private Discuss Chrome Extension allows users to schedule meetings directly from Chrome Browser. With the click of a button, you can start an instant meeting or schedule a future meeting. The meeting URL and information are available to copy and paste in any email or communication invitation so the attendee can join with a single-click.  

Private Discuss Chrome Extension allows you to:
•  Start an instant meeting
•  Schedule a future meeting
•  List your meetings of the day
